data.description: Honey, stop the car! Introducing this turn-key/pride of ownership in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Saugus. Enjoy this corner lot home oozing with curb appeal. Walking in, you will notice the vaulted ceiling, which is great for the sunlight to go through. The house has an excellent spacious floor plan and a seamless transition from the kitchen to the backyard, ideal for entertainment. The home features a spacious primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and remodeled primary restroom. Other upgrades include a remodeled kitchen and new paint in the living, dining, and family rooms. New tile and lighting in the kitchen and living room, an upgraded tankless water heater, and a water filtration system. Upgraded 5-ton AC unit along with an upgraded furnace system and fan circulation system to keep the electric bill low, a detached storage room and a new pergola patio.
